## Link Buttons

Buttons can function as links by adding the `href` attribute:

### Internal Links
{% button value="Go to Home" href="/" variant="primary" /%}
{% button value="View Documentation" href="/docs" variant="secondary" /%}
{% button value="See Examples" href="/docs/examples/alerts" variant="outline" /%}

### External Links
External links automatically get an icon and proper attributes:

{% button value="Visit GitHub" href="https://github.com" target="_blank" variant="primary" /%}
{% button value="View on NPM" href="https://npmjs.com" target="_blank" variant="secondary" /%}
{% button value="Documentation" href="https://docs.example.com" target="_blank" variant="outline" /%}
{% button value="API Reference" href="https://api.example.com" target="_blank" variant="ghost" /%}

