## Accessibility Features

All buttons include:
- Proper focus states with visible outlines
- Keyboard navigation support
- Semantic button/link elements
- External link indicators with `rel="noopener noreferrer"`
- Screen reader friendly attributes

## Best Practices

{% alert value="<strong>Use appropriate variants:</strong> Primary for main actions, secondary for alternatives, outline for subtle actions, and ghost for minimal interactions." type="info" /%}

{% alert value="<strong>Size considerations:</strong> Use large buttons for important CTAs, medium for standard actions, and small for secondary or space-constrained areas." type="info" /%}

{% alert value="<strong>External links:</strong> Always set <code>target='_blank'</code> for external links to open in new tabs with proper security attributes." type="warning" /%}
